Quickstrike:





"Dang," Quickstrike watched as Battera flew off. It was too late to shoot at 
her now. He grumbled with his head now. He steppped out, watching her. He 
slowly turned and walked back inside the cave. He turned his crimson optics 
to Dark Mouse as she said KitKat was in the new Predacon territory.

"What?" he snapped at her. "What's she doin' out there?"
